TITLE: Initializing PocketBase AuthStore from Cookie in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to load PocketBase AuthStore data from a cookie string and export it back to a cookie. These methods are useful for SSR integrations.
SOURCE: https://github.com/pocketbase/js-sdk/blob/master/README.md#2025-04-18_snippet_18

