TITLE: Creating a Custom Auth Store
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to create a custom authentication store by extending the BaseAuthStore class, allowing for custom business logic when handling authentication.
SOURCE: https://github.com/pocketbase/js-sdk/blob/master/README.md#2025-04-18_snippet_12

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
import PocketBase, { BaseAuthStore } from 'pocketbase';

class CustomAuthStore extends BaseAuthStore {
    save(token, model) {
        super.save(token, model);

        // your custom business logic...
    }
}

const pb = new PocketBase('http://127.0.0.1:8090', new CustomAuthStore());
```

